{"product_id":"upcircle-beauty-face-moisturiser-with-vitamin-e-aloe-vera-travel-size-30ml","title":"UpCircle Beauty Face Moisturiser with Vitamin E + Aloe Vera - Travel Size 30ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eThis multi award-winning vegan face moisturiser is suitable for all skin types. Vitamin E rich argan powder is combined with skin-soothing cocoa butter, aloe vera and blood orange.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eInspiring, upcycling, uplifting: This dermatologically approved face cream is made with finely-ground powder of discarded argan shells, a natural by-product of the argan oil industry and rich in antioxidant Vitamin E.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWinner of the \"Responsible Beauty\" award in the CEW Awards 2022, \"Best Moisturiser\" in the Natural Health Beauty Awards 2021. Winner in the Beauty Shortlist Awards 2021.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAn UpCircle Bestseller now perfectly packaged into a 30ml travel friendly format, great for any getaway.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply to clean, dry skin. Massage in until the cream absorbs. Suitable for all skin types and for daily use.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter, Glycerin, C14-22 Alcohols, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil*, Vitis Vinifera (Grape) Seed Oil, Cucumis Sativus (Cucumber) Fruit Extract*, Xanthan Gum, Coffea Arabica (Coffee) Seed Extract, Acer Rubrum (Maple) Extract, Sodium Hyaluronate, Olea Europaea (Olive) Fruit Oil, Calendula Officinalis Extract*, Rosmarinus Officinalis (Rosemary) Leaf Extract*, Anthemis Nobilis (Chamomile) Flower Oil, Tocopherol, Sodium Hydroxide, C12-20 Alkyl Glucoside, Potassium Sorbate, Sorbic Acid, Citric Acid, Sodium Benzoate, Salicylic Acid, Benzyl Alcohol, Limonene**. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*Organically grown ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e**Natural constituent of essential oils listed.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e99% NATURAL INGREDIENTS\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eHandmade | Social Good | Recycled Materials | Zero Waste | Cruelty Free | Vegan | Natural Resources | Non Toxic\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"UpCircle Beauty","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51133263118663,"sku":null,"price":14.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/upcircle-beauty-face-moisturiser-with-vitamin-e-aloe-vera-travel-size-30ml-234246.png?v=1740808672","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/upcircle-beauty-face-moisturiser-with-vitamin-e-aloe-vera-travel-size-30ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}